<html lang='en'>
	<head>
		<meta charset='UTF-8' />
		<meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
		<title>Post Update</title>
		<style>
			body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0;
			background-color: #f5f5f5; display: flex; justify-content: center; }
			.container { width: 100%; max-width: 600px; background-color: #fff;
			border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 20px; margin: 40px; border-radius: 8px; }
			.header { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px;
			text-align: center; color: #2c3e50; } .greeting { font-size: 18px;
			margin-bottom: 15px; } .content { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;
			color: #4a4a4a; margin-bottom: 20px; } .btn { display: inline-block;
			padding: 10px 15px; background-color: #B08968; color: #fff;
			text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; text-align: center;
			font-weight: bold; margin: 20px auto; display: block; } .footer {
			font-size: 14px; color: #888; text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; }
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class='container'>
			<div class='header'>Speak About It</div>
			<p class='greeting'>Hello, {{name}}!</p>
			<p class='content'>
				We wanted to let you know that a post youâ€™re following has been updated.
			</p>
			<p class='content'>
				<strong>Post Title:</strong>
				{{title}}
			</p>
			<a href='{{url}}' class='btn'>View Updated Post</a>
			<div class='footer'>
				<p>Thank you for being a part of Speak About It.</p>
				<p>We hope this update is valuable to you!</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>